        <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review it periodically.</p>

        <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@nutriconnect.com">support@nutriconnect.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>